    $translate['en']['abilities_vr2_desc'] = "It all started with a minor fund-raising event for manufacturing the first prototype of Oculus Rift goggles. The fund-raising even was hosted on the Kickstarter site. Since then almost everyone see huge potential in the recent invention. 
